      <blockquote class="pullquote" data-reveal data-delay="2">
        Marketing teams in auto insurance are being asked to evaluate
        digital-twin vendors without a practitioner-grade definition of the
        technology — this project tries to supply one, anchored in primary
        survey evidence and a working prototype.
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== STACK / TOOLING ===== -->
  <section class="section section--alt" aria-labelledby="stack-h">
    <div class="container container-narrow">
