      <ul class="list-clean" data-reveal data-delay="2">
        <li><strong>HTML, CSS, vanilla JS</strong> — the hub you're on, hand-written, no framework. Live now.</li>
        <li><strong>Flourish</strong> — data visualization powering the D1 survey dashboard, live at <a href="https://jade-salamander-5559d4.netlify.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener">jade-salamander-5559d4.netlify.app ↗</a>.</li>
        <li><strong>Netlify</strong> — hosting for the D1 dashboard and the D2 long-read zine at <a href="https://digitaltwinszeen.netlify.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener">digitaltwinszeen.netlify.app ↗</a>.</li>
        <li><strong>Unity (WebGL)</strong> — the D3 decision simulator, upcoming.</li>
        <li><strong>Figma</strong> — layout, type, and the D2 zine artwork.</li>
        <li><strong>GitHub Pages</strong> — static hosting for this hub, open-source repo.</li>
        <li><strong>GA4</strong> — analytics, gated behind a consent banner.</li>
        <li><strong>APA 7</strong> — citation style across all artifacts.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

